<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>emsenn.net</title><link>https://emsenn.net/library/spirituality/domains/divination/domains/tarot/</link><description>Recent content on emsenn.net</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://emsenn.net/library/spirituality/domains/divination/domains/tarot/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Tarot ideas</title><link>https://emsenn.net/library/spirituality/domains/divination/domains/tarot/ideas/</link><pubDate>Wed, 31 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://emsenn.net/library/spirituality/domains/divination/domains/tarot/ideas/</guid><description>&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add per-card documents with upright/reversed interpretations and sources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add structured spreads beyond three-card and Celtic cross.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Tarot plans</title><link>https://emsenn.net/library/spirituality/domains/divination/domains/tarot/plans/</link><pubDate>Wed, 31 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://emsenn.net/library/spirituality/domains/divination/domains/tarot/plans/</guid><description>&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build full per-card documentation for all 78 cards with citations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add spread YAML schema validation and rendering templates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Tarot specifications</title><link>https://emsenn.net/library/spirituality/domains/divination/domains/tarot/specifications/</link><pubDate>Wed, 31 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://emsenn.net/library/spirituality/domains/divination/domains/tarot/specifications/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This specification defines how tarot data is encoded for spreads and readings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="spread-yaml"&gt;Spread YAML&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Required keys:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;spread&lt;/code&gt;: name of the spread.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;positions&lt;/code&gt;: ordered list of position definitions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;draw&lt;/code&gt;: list of cards drawn with positions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Each position includes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;name&lt;/code&gt;: position label.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;role&lt;/code&gt;: meaning or function in the spread.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Each draw entry includes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;position&lt;/code&gt;: position name.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;card&lt;/code&gt;: card name.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;orientation&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;upright&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;reversed&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;spread&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;three-card&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;positions&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;past&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;role&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;the background or origin&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;present&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;role&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;the current situation&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;future&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;role&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;a likely direction&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;draw&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;position&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;past&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;card&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;The Fool&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;orientation&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;upright&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;position&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;present&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;card&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;Two of Cups&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;orientation&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;upright&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;position&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;future&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;card&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;The Tower&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;orientation&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;reversed&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>